{"tid":248370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印尼軍演，中國製大炮失控亂射，四死八傷","createTime":"2017-05-18T13:36:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-20T03:09:49.000Z","uid":79563,"like":75,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"283b1974fe3b3680d71d4ea98da235cc08dadf26","tid":248370,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T13:36:21.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">印尼軍演，中國製大炮失控亂射，四死八傷</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2017/05/17/four-killed-eight-wounded-in-natuna-military-exercise-gone-wrong.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thejakartapost.com%2Fnews%2F2017%2F05%2F17%2Ffour-killed-eight-wounded-in-natuna-military-exercise-gone-wrong.html&d=sJi30nZJaTuGAzS5CtepdACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=037c8e4a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2017/05/17/four-killed-eight-wounded-in-natuna-military-exercise-gone-wrong.html</a><br />\n<br />\nFour killed, eight wounded in Natuna military exercise gone wrong<br />\nA Chinese-made cannon malfunctioned and fired off shots randomly during military exercises in Tanjung Datuk, Natuna, Riau Islands province, on Wednesday. Four soldiers were killed and eight were wounded.<br />\nDuring the exercises, held by an Indonesian Army quick response team (PPRC TNI AD) at the Air Defense Artillery 1/K compound, soldiers were undergoing target practice with the Giant Bow cannon.<br />\n<br />\nThe exercises were reportedly part of preparations ahead of a May 19 event during which a military parade will be conducted in front of President Joko &ldquo;Jokowi&rdquo; Widodo.<br />\n<br />\nHowever, Army spokesperson Col. Alfret Denny Tuejeh denied the exercises were connected to a parade, saying they were just regular exercises. He had previously confirmed that the incident occurred during a &ldquo;rehearsal.&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;The incident occurred during the second round of exercises [on Wednesday],&rdquo; he said on Wednesday, adding that the incident happened at about 11 a.m.<br />\n<br />\nThe gears &quot;malfunctioned,&quot; Denny said.<br />\nThe first round of exercises proceeded smoothly, he said.<br />\nDenny said there were 12 victims, including the four fatalities. The eight wounded soldiers were taken to Natuna General Hospital (RSUD Natuna). <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2071570\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2071570&d=sJi30nZJaTuGAzS5CtepdACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=a6b394bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2071570&h=c4d17d6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2071570</a><br />\n印尼軍演傳意外4死8傷 軍方：中國製火砲失控<br />\n印尼海軍昨天進行演習，過程中一門火砲突然失控，造成4死、8傷意外，事後官方表示，該門火砲是向中國購買，在演習前仍可正常測試。<br />\n<br />\n《雅加達郵報》報導，印尼海軍昨天在廖內群島（Riau Islands）的納圖納（Natuna）進行射擊演訓，過程一門「巨型弓炮」突然失靈，造成4名士兵死亡、8人受傷送醫。報導指出，昨天演訓是為了19日的正式軍演進行準備工作，明天印尼總統將參與操演。<br />\n<br />\n印尼軍方發言人泰耶爾（Alfret Denny Tuejeh）表示，軍演為定期進行，事件發生在第二輪演習，時間約在昨天上午11點左右。他補充，該門失控火砲齒輪故障。<br />\n<br />\n軍方表示，這門火砲購於2003年，為中國製造，在演習前一天仍可正常測試，目前正在調查意外原因。"},{"pid":"2646f1c3f03bfeb69975d825941748c19d759971","tid":248370,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T13:37:25.000Z","msg":"要用火藥既野都敢買中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a68eaec56281869bf6b68985703d5bea4b6e7cc3","tid":248370,"uid":98692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T13:37:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />2003買"},{"pid":"34df149ec270106f5d422dac0c00976ae9e18870","tid":248370,"uid":12393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T13:55:13.000Z","msg":"不戰而屈人之兵"},{"pid":"e2c23a358ee7aff7489cbed1ff54379990439a83","tid":248370,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T13:57:52.000Z","msg":"據《簡氏防務周刊》報道，近期印尼總統視察印尼海軍「爪窪艦隊」2016年演習的時候，兩枚新採購的中國C-705反艦導彈試射過程均出現「故障問題」，引起軒然大波！讓「中國造」頓時成為了世界軍迷們討論的風口浪尖。當然，中國軍友們反擊流言蜚語的聲音也多不勝數。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n那麼到底是「中國造」反艦導彈出現了問題，還是印尼海軍不熟悉操作流程導致發射失敗？<br />\n其實在報道中，當時印尼海軍號兩艘KCR-40型導彈艇分別發射一枚C-705導彈。我們可以看出來，印尼海軍的KCR-40型導彈艇是印尼自主研製的一款導彈艇，可以裝載兩枚C-705導彈。最早中國造的C-705導彈和俄制「寶石」反艦導彈都是印尼護衛艦和導彈艇的艦載武器選項，最終對於印尼來說，KCR-40型導彈艇，更像是擅長近戰的「海上突擊隊員」，最終選擇了搭載便宜些的C-705型反艦導彈。而護衛艦則選擇了更加貴一些的俄制「寶石」反艦導彈。"},{"pid":"6c037dcf2614698ebf147c78248afeec2a84c10c","tid":248370,"uid":3191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T13:59:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不戰而屈人之兵</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1742fd2d5a904a87c8a07054cef113847b9ee6aa","tid":248370,"uid":35696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T14:02:32.000Z","msg":"明明地區最大敵人就係支那<br />\n仲要搵支那買軍備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a00c24950d49c28313c9df3b0c7aaeffa6b47316","tid":248370,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T14:06:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">印尼軍演，中國製大炮失控亂射，四死八傷</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2017/05/17/four-killed-eight-wounded-in-natuna-military-exercise-gone-wrong.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thejakartapost.com%2Fnews%2F2017%2F05%2F17%2Ffour-killed-eight-wounded-in-natuna-military-exercise-gone-wrong.html&d=sJi30nZJaTuGAzS5CtepdACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=037c8e4a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2017/05/17/four-killed-eight-wounded-in-natuna-military-exercise-gone-wrong.html</a><br />\n<br />\nFour killed, eight wounded in Natuna military exercise gone wrong<br />\nA Chinese-made cannon malfunctioned and fired off shots randomly during military exercises in Tanjung